[VS2-333] Data Collection sources

Background:
Data that is provisioned to User may come from variety of sources. Many cases include different data modality of the same Study being sourced from multiple sources. These source systems must be explicitly mapped to data modalities to support the data delivery method requirements and enable proper policy layer configuration.

User Story:
As a Data Owner/Delegate Data Owner, I want to specify data sources for each Data Collection so that data sourcing and access are clearly defined.

Acceptance criteria:
GIVEN defined data modality for a Study WHEN the source system for it is defined THEN selection of data source for each data modality is enabled.
GIVEN defined data modality for a Study WHEN it is configured THEN no blank data source for each modality is present.
GIVEN multiple data modalities for a Study WHEN source systems are defined THEN each modality-to-source mapping is recorded.